org.jenkinsci.plugins.github.pullrequest.title: Rename external representation of Statistical History (JDK11)
org.jenkinsci.plugins.github.pullrequest.body:
Rename "Statistical History" to "Vitals" with a minimum of fuss:

fixes #420
